nodes.text: Baranj the Starseeker was a Evocii male Rifle Grenadier and sharpshooter who lived on Nal Hutta during the Cold War. He and a group of other Evocii had acquired a starship, which was cause for alarm for the Hutt Cartel. Rhamm, one of Suudaa Nem'ro's foremen, tasked an individual with killing Baranj and his followers as well as destroying the starship.
